                    <h3>For International Sellers (UAE & KSA)</h3>
                </div>
                <ul class="docs-list">
                    <li>Note: Egypt does not allow international sellers to sell</li>
                    <li>Trade licence (30-day validity; company registered outside UAE/KSA)</li>
                    <li>VAT Certificate (issued in the UAE/KSA)</li>
                    <li>Valid identity proof (Passport)</li>
                    <li>Bank account details (Payoneer or LoanLoan account, duly signed and stamped with company seal)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- Indian Sellers (Global Store) -->
