                    <li>GST Certificate</li>
                    <li>Bank Account Proof (Cancelled Cheque / Authorized Statement)</li>
                    <li>Authorized Signatory Name, Email ID, and Mobile Number</li>
                    <li>PAN &amp; Aadhaar (Authorized Signatory / Director)</li>
                    <li>Product catalog with minimum 50 SKUs (with barcodes &amp; Transfer Price)</li>
                    <li>No IEC or AD Code required</li>
