    <!-- Noon Seller Onboarding Process -->
    <section class="process-section" id="process">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>The Process for Noon Seller Account Onboarding</h2>
            <p class="subtitle">A straightforward 5-step process to get you live on Noon</p>
        </div>
        <div class="steps-container">
            <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>Register Your Seller Account</h3>
                    <p>Go to the Sell with Noon page and click on the "Register Now" option to be redirected to the Noon partner page.</p>
                    <ul class="step-sub-list">
                        <li>Enter a valid email ID and phone number, and verify with an OTP</li>
                        <li>Choose a unique organisation name to get your organisation ID</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>Set Up Your Noon Store</h3>
                    <p>After your organisation ID is created, Noon will direct you to the store creation page. If not directed, go to the Welcome page and click on "sell on Noon.com".</p>
                    <ul class="step-sub-list">
                        <li>Add store details: country, display name, active email, phone number, and product category</li>
                        <li>Once submitted, Noon will create your seller store so you can list products</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>Choose the Fulfilment Model</h3>
                    <p>Noon offers two types of fulfilment models — choose the right one for your business:</p>
                    <ul class="step-sub-list">
                        <li><strong>Fulfilled by Noon (FBN):</strong> Noon picks, packs, and delivers your products to customers</li>
                        <li><strong>Fulfilled by Partner:</strong> You pack and ship with the help of a third-party logistics provider</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>Wait for the Verification Process</h3>
                    <p>After completing the above steps, Noon's support team will review and verify your documents. This typically takes 4–5 working days.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">5</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h3>Start Selling</h3>
                    <p>Once documents are verified, products are listed, and the fulfilment model is approved, customers can start placing orders and you will begin generating revenue.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

